# NOTICE

Buddies Onchain bundles two third-party fonts. The WOFF2 payloads are embedded
in the on-chain SVG renderer (committed under `onchain/contract-data/fonts/`)
and reused in the social-card SVGs under `site/tools/og/`. Both licenses are
permissive; the full text of each ships alongside its font.

The font payloads travel with the deployed contract bytecode. Anyone who
redeploys or forks the contract redistributes these font payloads — this
NOTICE and the corresponding license files must travel with such forks.

